#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:115
#: src/Common/templates/partials/full-lpa-display.html.twig:140
msgid "Attorneys must make decisions jointly (together)"
msgstr "Rhaid i atwrneiod wneud penderfyniadau ar y cyd (gyda’i gilydd)"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:117
#: src/Common/templates/partials/full-lpa-display.html.twig:142
msgid "Attorneys can make decisions jointly (together) and severally (separately)"
msgstr ""
"Gall atwrneiod wneud penderfyniadau ar y cyd (gyda’i gilydd) neu yn annibynnol "
"ar ei gilydd (ar wahân)"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:119
msgid ""
"Attorneys must make some decisions jointly (together) and can make some "
"decisions severally (separately). Check the paper <abbr title=\"lasting power of "
"attorney\">LPA</abbr> to find out what decisions must be made jointly."
msgstr ""
"Rhaid i atwrneiod wneud rhai penderfyniadau ar y cyd (gyda’i gilydd) ac maent yn "
"gallu gwneud rhai penderfyniadau yn annibynnol ar ei gilydd (ar wahân) Gwiriwch "
"yr <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth arhosol\">LPA</abbr> papur i gael gwybod pa "
"benderfyniadau y mae’n rhaid eu gwneud ar y cyd."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:146
