"Yes, the donor set instructions on their <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney"
"\">LPA</abbr>.<br>To view these, ask to see the paper <abbr title=\"lasting "
"power of attorney\">LPA</abbr>"
msgstr ""
"Do, mae’r rhoddwr wedi rhoi cyfarwyddiadau yn ei <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth "
"arhosol\">LPA</abbr>. I weld y rhain, gofynnwch am gael gweld y <abbr title="
"\"atwrneiaeth arhosol\">LPA</abbr> papur"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:185
msgid "When can the <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> be used?"
msgstr ""
"Pa bryd y gellir defnyddio’r <abbr title=\"atwrneiaeth arhosol\">LPA</abbr>?"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:189
